attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Step inside this thoughtfully designed townhome, where high-end upgrades shine throughout. The open-concept top floor showcases custom millwork, premium finishes, and abundant natural light. A private elevator ensures seamless access to every level. The chef’s kitchen stuns with Sub Zero and Wolf appliances, custom cabinetry, and a large island perfect for entertaining. The primary suite is a true retreat with a five-piece ensuite and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms offer flexibility, while a bonus room serves as an office with a murphy bed. A private garage provides hassle-free parking. Just steps from the newly updated Lago Playground, scenic beaches, and South Boston’s top dining and shopping, this townhome offers luxury and convenience in a prime location.
